# Netflix Data Analysis 📺

## 📌 Project Overview
Analyzed Netflix dataset to uncover insights about content trends, genres, ratings, and release patterns.

## 🎯 Objectives..
- Understand content distribution (Movies vs TV Shows)
- Analyze most popular genres
- Identify trends in content release over years
- Study country-wise content production

## 🛠 Tools & Technologies..
- Python (Pandas, NumPy, Matplotlib, Seaborn)
- Jupyter Notebook
- SQL (optional)
- Excel

## 📊 Key Insights
- Movies dominate Netflix content compared to TV Shows
- Drama and Comedy are the most popular genres
- Significant growth in content after 2015
- USA produces the highest number of titles

